description: Deletes the specified member accounts from Security Hub. You can invoke this API only to delete accounts that became members through invitation. You can't invoke this API to delete accounts that belong to an Organizations organization.

nested_items.name: UnprocessedAccounts
nested_items.description: The list of Amazon Web Services accounts that were not deleted. For each account, the list includes the account ID and the email address.

nested_items.name: AccountId
nested_items.description: An Amazon Web Services account ID of the account that was not processed.

nested_items.name: ProcessingResult
nested_items.description: The reason that the account was not processed.
